A '''Workgang''' is a group of individuals who are assigned, or engaged in, a common task.
Examples include Prison Workgangs used for [[farming]], [[construction]], [[Trash (material)|trash]] collection/[[waste management]], [[fire fighting]], or inmate [[emergency services]].
Such workgangs have varying levels of supervision ranging from Armed [[Corrections Officer]]s, Unarmed '''Community Supervision''', to self-supervised [[Trustee]]s.

